description: Returns metadata of the User such as UserID in the specified collection. Anonymous User (to reserve faces without any identity) is not returned as part of this request. The results are sorted by system generated primary key ID. If the response is truncated, NextToken is returned in the response that can be used in the subsequent request to retrieve the next set of identities.

parameters.name: CollectionId
parameters.description: The ID of an existing collection.

nested_items.name: Users
nested_items.description: List of UsersID associated with the specified collection.

nested_items.name: UserId
nested_items.description: A provided ID for the User. Unique within the collection.

nested_items.name: UserStatus
nested_items.description: Communicates if the UserID has been updated with latest set of faces to be associated with the UserID.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A pagination token to be used with the subsequent request if the response is truncated.
